Description: Cordite Wars: Six Fronts
 Command six distinct factions across land, air, and sea in a real-time
 strategy game inspired by Command & Conquer and Tempest Rising.
 .
 Features deterministic multiplayer, full cross-platform support, and four
 graphical quality tiers for broad hardware compatibility.
 .
